warp_1=`/*
warp_2=`Volumetric Lines by Inigo Quilez
warp_3=`Converted from ShaderToy to MilkDrop by DeepSeek, modified by me
warp_4=`Original ShaderToy shader link: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4slGz4
warp_5=`*/
warp_6=`
warp_7=`/*
warp_8=`Inigo Quilez:
